articles.title: Missing fisherman was dragged overboard by shark entangled in fishing gear, Australian police say - CBS News
articles.description: Paul Barning went missing Sunday after falling overboard his boat during a fishing competition in New South Wales, Australia.
articles.content:
Police in Australia say a fisherman who fell overboard during a fishing competition on Sunday was dragged by a shark that was entangled in fishing gear.
